Package: whitehouse.gov
Title: OMB Historical Budget Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for OMB Historical Budget Tables from
    whitehouse.gov. Covers budget totals, receipts, outlays, budget authority,
    debt, and economic indicators from 1789 to present. Includes LLM context
    injection via omb_context().
